== Overview ==
A very powerful weapon feared throughout the [[Gamma Sector]] and utilized to devastating effect.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Peace Maker Cannon is rewarded as a consolation prize to any Controller who completes the Brotherhood Temple quest but fails to do so before any other Controller.
